	"""OP : Specifies which [[Geometry COMP|Geometry]] will be included in the rendered scene. You can use [[Pattern Matching]] to specify objects using patterns. Example: ```geo*  ^geo7</code> will render all Geometry components whose names start with <code>geo</code> except <code>geo7```."""
